{"tid":129132,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有養貓狗寵物既巴絲入唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-21T11:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T15:41:12.000Z","uid":80662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bef245934c74b2d93a9d61bd3db1f0844302dc5","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"如果自己既寵物(其他寵物都可以) 有朝突然離開人世，你地會點做？<br />\n繼續養下一隻？<br />\n定係唔再養？<br />\n有冇過來人分享吓生離死別既經驗？"},{"pid":"8d9aa80ea48ad15c533f7911e8b386a2507e18bb","tid":129132,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先整個相架 frame 起張合照"},{"pid":"4915cf46d3f2dbff843e1de34a294b5b54b090eb","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先整個相架 frame 起張合照</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未整你講起已經咸左出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cec5f480c6e5b2226937c5b81dfc1d621efefde","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先整個相架 frame 起張合照</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未整你講起已經咸左出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n激動到字都睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咸左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc6d79ef35173b1becf85ffd79f35734a3857c4","tid":129132,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"第一隻貓只係陪左我8年，由發病到死只係一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n病發嗰陣已經有心理準備，但都喊左成日<br />\n之後無咩意欲再養，過左6、7年放低左先再養番"},{"pid":"5c056550d9a4152214a985fd0e763bb6ec4f425b","tid":129132,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"之前養過隻天竺鼠 養左成年 後尾佢有腫瘤死咗 之後嗰一年諗起就哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家有時諗返都會哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n隔左2-3年就開始養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家佢3歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d90351f4d6c6e7ef5744168d1664cc52eb59c3c","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一隻貓只係陪左我8年，由發病到死只係一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n病發嗰陣已經有心理準備，但都喊左成日<br />\n之後無咩意欲再養，過左6、7年放低左先再養番</blockquote><br />\n我隻貓8 個月已經有深厚感情，何況你係8 年，好難想像你既情感，我依家好似走左個親人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e9d7a603b300918b782178c3905ec26b8da454","tid":129132,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"會繼續領養，幫得一隻得一隻<br />\n<br />\n利申前後四隻貓，而家得返兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a79bffb543b26c3577d2a83d324e9429095a6bb","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前養過隻天竺鼠 養左成年 後尾佢有腫瘤死咗 之後嗰一年諗起就哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家有時諗返都會哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n隔左2-3年就開始養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家佢3歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實冇勇氣再養下一隻貓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我心入面又想養一隻貓仔黎治療我對「牠」的思念。<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾，唔養既話，我日常生活入面好似少左一樣野咁。"},{"pid":"867ecc94c22cff67e24b6c81fac84a8c1a203f24","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會繼續領養，幫得一隻得一隻<br />\n<br />\n利申前後四隻貓，而家得返兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，再養其實又係折磨自己，大吉利是又黎多次，我真係企唔返起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff84452e46c808626f6bd60d75e29d98f57015a7","tid":129132,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"會養多隻<br />\n但唔係用黎代替死左果隻"},{"pid":"a60d616879396551b20340d5d5253dbc6d2d877d","tid":129132,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"寵物走咗後，個心好似穿咗洞，人都變得迷茫。<br />\n雖然，領養咗隻狗，本住將愛延續落去。<br />\n現實後佢走咗大半年，每當諗起佢都喊。仍然未放低。<br />\n樓主，如果你擔心有呢一日，請定時backup 啲相。我嗰陣無做，有啲相喺舊電腦度，部腦死咗，累到啲相無咗。"},{"pid":"2d00a425c2f52ab9ec21923934f9f55cc0b700a8","tid":129132,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前養過隻天竺鼠 養左成年 後尾佢有腫瘤死咗 之後嗰一年諗起就哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家有時諗返都會哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n隔左2-3年就開始養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家佢3歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實冇勇氣再養下一隻貓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我心入面又想養一隻貓仔黎治療我對「牠」的思念。<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾，唔養既話，我日常生活入面好似少左一樣野咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開頭嗰陣係好唔慣 好希望只係發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽講你一路掛住佢 佢會唔捨得走 會跟住自己<br />\n<br />\n之前一路都有發夢見到以前隻鼠 後尾養咗而家隻狗就發夢見到佢咬我手指咬到流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n隻鼠一路都好乖 未試過咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n之後無再發夢見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdb6e871a45e20f5dc32cbdbe77aca9b351e771","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會養多隻<br />\n但唔係用黎代替死左果隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係過來人？<br />\n 可能我仲未去到你既階段，我知如果再養多隻係對新寵物唔公平，但真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己偏向唔會再養。唔想再傷多次，<br />\n出post只係想知道大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6e456cddc9072c4b97c6e5c54312a69382b7e3","tid":129132,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會養多隻<br />\n但唔係用黎代替死左果隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係過來人？<br />\n 可能我仲未去到你既階段，我知如果再養多隻係對新寵物唔公平，但真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己偏向唔會再養。唔想再傷多次，<br />\n出post只係想知道大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企原本有3隻貓 <br />\n一隻老母 一隻仔 同女 <br />\n個女有日心臟有事 係屋企狂跑 之後心臟病去左<br />\n仲要係我房個角位大叫左一聲先死<br />\n唔開心直到火化左佢 覺得佢死左都係好事<br />\n因為由bb開始已經唔足磅 腳又有事 成日病 <br />\n希望佢下一世會健康d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔養會好唔習慣 屋企少左舊野行黎行去"},{"pid":"d992f978d52c33f5b8e1d0caed36b367dd9c9816","tid":129132,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會繼續領養，幫得一隻得一隻<br />\n<br />\n利申前後四隻貓，而家得返兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，再養其實又係折磨自己，大吉利是又黎多次，我真係企唔返起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你用幫助既心態去做就唔同<br />\n<br />\n你諗下而家岀面咁凍，d浪浪飢寒交迫幾可憐<br />\n如果你帶佢返屋企，用少少多餘既愛就可以改變佢一生"},{"pid":"b0b96f3d0f7fee69ca1979f51976771475cffbd5","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會養多隻<br />\n但唔係用黎代替死左果隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係過來人？<br />\n 可能我仲未去到你既階段，我知如果再養多隻係對新寵物唔公平，但真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己偏向唔會再養。唔想再傷多次，<br />\n出post只係想知道大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企原本有3隻貓 <br />\n一隻老母 一隻仔 同女 <br />\n個女有日心臟有事 係屋企狂跑 之後心臟病去左<br />\n仲要係我房個角位大叫左一聲先死<br />\n唔開心直到火化左佢 覺得佢死左都係好事<br />\n因為由bb開始已經唔足磅 腳又有事 成日病 <br />\n希望佢下一世會健康d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔養會好唔習慣 屋企少左舊野行黎行去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，冇舊野行黎行去，真係唔慣。。。好似少左樣野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7f4ebd6ee154ec5a8f6f40a6ba72ffb7dd987c","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n但你用幫助既心態去做就唔同<br />\n<br />\n你諗下而家岀面咁凍，d浪浪飢寒交迫幾可憐<br />\n如果你帶佢返屋企，用少少多餘既愛就可以改變佢一生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都講得o岩既，唯有隨緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73912c2a686690a3f08278cd8df78969d986f43","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開頭嗰陣係好唔慣 好希望只係發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但聽講你一路掛住佢 佢會唔捨得走 會跟住自己</span><br />\n<br />\n之前一路都有發夢見到以前隻鼠 後尾養咗而家隻狗就發夢見到佢咬我手指咬到流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n隻鼠一路都好乖 未試過咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n之後無再發夢見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你o係邊聽返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你feel到？"},{"pid":"97371e3de7485d59ee9d85ead5571f52eeefdbc7","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物走咗後，個心好似穿咗洞，人都變得迷茫。<br />\n雖然，領養咗隻狗，本住將愛延續落去。<br />\n現實後佢走咗大半年，每當諗起佢都喊。仍然未放低。<br />\n樓主，如果你擔心有呢一日，請定時backup 啲相。我嗰陣無做，有啲相喺舊電腦度，部腦死咗，累到啲相無咗。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家經歷緊你講d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢d相我有backup, 多謝提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4bef8805c28e6affa9187a212ecf6a6e2f7182","tid":129132,"uid":77554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"屋企四貓一狗 狗仔十五歲年初一凌晨4點幾走左 即刻打電話去終於有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都預計到..<br />\n前幾年隻貓得3歳 又係凌晨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51ae9854d53a71068eb31bdbd903f03a4ca11ac","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企四貓一狗 狗仔十五歲年初一凌晨4點幾走左 即刻打電話去終於有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都預計到..<br />\n前幾年隻貓得3歳 又係凌晨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你失去兩隻都仲有三隻可以有精神寄托，<br />\n雖然邊隻冇左都係唔想架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我本身養開一隻，冇左就係冇左。"},{"pid":"4f9feab680103307877708f726e12ba637bfa886","tid":129132,"uid":86732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"會再養 仲要同種 個樣要似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2f225c92142eb6df20479bd75569a51414ae52","tid":129132,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會再養 仲要同種 個樣要似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣對現任唔係幾fair喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff18a54465700f335a9ba949340aa0540c71a082","tid":129132,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"養緊隻貓8個月大，已經成日諗日後佢死左會唔會再養<br />\n雖然我傾向想繼續養，有能力養多幾隻仲好，因為太多浪浪需要照顧<br />\n但一諗到好驚接下一隻返黎會成日拎佢黎同死左果隻比較，覺得鍾意以前果隻多好多咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畢竟依家隻貓係我第一隻貓，仲要佢2星期大就執左返屋企養，細個每幾個鐘餵奶放屎尿抱住氹佢瞓，眠乾碎濕湊大佢當正親生仔，好怕依家太深既羈絆令我日後再養唔到其他貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}